Package: mlogitsel
Type: Package
Title: Multinomial Logit Model with Sample Selection
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Your", "Name", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements a two-step estimator for multinomial logit models with 
    sample selection bias. The package handles situations where outcomes are only 
    observed for a non-random subset of the population, such as employment sector 
    choice observed only for labor force participants. Includes multiplier bootstrap
    for inference.
